{"tid":490252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]矛盾對決: 煮飯VS洗碗","createTime":"2017-12-05T12:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T21:05:19.000Z","uid":161709,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7d26ff57b31f247b288406baddc0f81aa4428b","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"日日洗碗都要聽住My Chemical Romance, <br />\n煮飯係辛苦, 但煮一餐飯, 實在太多嘢要洗, 碗碟都係油同汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉, 在在家千日好,出門半朝難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔識煮, 同屋住負責煮, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca3bb7ff526fc331db83af249d1ee6e4ab0389c","tid":490252,"uid":71373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"鍾意煮飯唔鍾意洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4b87e0daa8306fcca028478b6ae419b05115ac","tid":490252,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"煮飯有個人空間可以發揮下，簡單有簡單煮，一路煮好香<br />\n最緊要可以煮比屋企人食其實好開心<br />\n<br />\n洗就真係單純體力勞動，悶囉"},{"pid":"d92a2c13b371a8a4a2e2f60ea99aea444d1af384","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意煮飯唔鍾意洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企係咁嘅, 阿媽煮就阿爸洗, 阿爸煮就細佬洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人做晒就真係太辛苦"},{"pid":"ae95cad5f360752f43645ac57a05823556cf456e","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煮飯有個人空間可以發揮下，簡單有簡單煮，一路煮好香<br />\n最緊要可以煮比屋企人食其實好開心<br />\n<br />\n洗就真係單純體力勞動，悶囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家準備要洗啦, hea咗成粒鐘啦已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4389d3873a3cf4c5d6d05de9910b28ba3ff1bb5a","tid":490252,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了"},{"pid":"1848a554ac9e091c3a0eab08fb3ce1585fe5e183","tid":490252,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>煮飯有個人空間可以發揮下，簡單有簡單煮，一路煮好香<br />\n最緊要可以煮比屋企人食其實好開心<br />\n<br />\n洗就真係單純體力勞動，悶囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家準備要洗啦, hea咗成粒鐘啦已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日拖住唔洗住<br />\n俾老母屌到開花"},{"pid":"c27560cc1ad5dddb65e0d61c516dfe68e3365f59","tid":490252,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了</blockquote><br />\n啲膠手套 &quot;eat eat&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8438a3db4c400778fcc7f2451de060f222fa2ad9","tid":490252,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了</blockquote><br />\n啲膠手套 &quot;eat eat&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聲"},{"pid":"1e838c8d91f94b64623fe5531692225fee7ad6ef","tid":490252,"uid":20928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了</blockquote><br />\n點解洗碗要手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見啲人都帶不過我從來唔用手套洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c072d371075104aa5ba22d6770c771b6bec8fe0","tid":490252,"uid":401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"洗碗機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a749be2da16e492c94107f5be3a2c2b9135ea1d","tid":490252,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗碗機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9710d76feb3d06b952a74c87572d22f6ac11f25","tid":490252,"uid":130849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了</blockquote><br />\n點解洗碗要手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見啲人都帶不過我從來唔用手套洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 係咁沖水沖到隻手好'鞋' 同埋唔想直接掂到d油漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f659ac138aff2e76f37907ac673135fe9da0a46e","tid":490252,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"洗碗俾盡你咪兩三個字<br />\n十指不沾陽春水乸型黎<br />\n唔鍾意做叫人做自私精"},{"pid":"47bc73dfa059e8a4ed5a72aaf3a250c717b8b56b","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗碗俾盡你咪兩三個字<br />\n十指不沾陽春水乸型黎<br />\n唔鍾意做叫人做自私精</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇黎巴打好少煮飯同做家務<br />\n其實煮完飯嘅廚房係好污糟<br />\n三餸一湯其實唔只得五隻碗<br />\n仲要清潔爐頭同埋拖埋地嫁<br />\n唔洗碗其實仲要其他家務揀<br />\n雖然我唔鐘意洗但無話唔洗<br />\n<br />\nRelax喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e66d43f50b8f4bbf89297d28641d78084e13c57","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:18:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗碗機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家呢度仲有洗碗機, 但覺得洗完都油油地...要再洗多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625d4566cca2dfe18526afca11ce01965e9e0f43","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗碗機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家呢度<del>仲</del>有洗碗機, 但覺得洗完都油油地...要再洗多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都"},{"pid":"ffb24592cd86c11a0fc777b0943465fbac52942c","tid":490252,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"單以時間計，洗碗快煮飯好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f654024e621bfd2b87d3b2f614a721814520f5","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單以時間計，洗碗快煮飯好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 煮飯準備工夫好多, 洗洗切切都有排搞, <br />\n不過各有各辛苦啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977ab98db3cf8c2fe5142467ae37281a599582b1","tid":490252,"uid":20928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了</blockquote><br />\n點解洗碗要手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見啲人都帶不過我從來唔用手套洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 係咁沖水沖到隻手好'鞋' 同埋唔想直接掂到d油漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過帶手套好跣，又容易捉唔實啲碗，好易打爛嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔介意掂到油漬同食物殘渣，不過我隻手洗碗洗到皮膚好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c13b80e7d7298b961a2b57af48983e429e2f074","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗碗有手套我OK<br />\n無就不了</blockquote><br />\n點解洗碗要手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見啲人都帶不過我從來唔用手套洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 係咁沖水沖到隻手好'鞋' 同埋唔想直接掂到d油漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過帶手套好跣，又容易捉唔實啲碗，好易打爛嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔介意掂到油漬同食物殘渣，不過我隻手洗碗洗到皮膚好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用手套好難洗同埋feel唔到啲碗仲油唔油, 唯有洗完搽cream"},{"pid":"c90353a1c2ffe3f34d3b40d6d236e9a0c6dc6e4b","tid":490252,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:31:37.000Z","msg":"煮飯同洗碗都有人幫輕冭就好好多<br />\n<br />\n我負責煮我女朋友就幫手切下野<br />\n我女朋友洗我就抺枱洗爐頭同洗鑊<br />\n<br />\n咁就唔覺辛苦"},{"pid":"f1cecb15a85a3cfa7dd822a14316d886715632ca","tid":490252,"uid":161709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煮飯同洗碗都有人幫輕冭就好好多<br />\n<br />\n我負責煮我女朋友就幫手切下野<br />\n我女朋友洗我就抺枱洗爐頭同洗鑊<br />\n<br />\n咁就唔覺辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 呢個都係重點, <br />\n唔會覺得淨係得自己做, 又快啲搞掂"},{"pid":"f6532c0adca919f4ac47b25a7c5d0e483116739b","tid":490252,"uid":158371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"寧願煮都唔洗"},{"pid":"fde5ef4c59bb8d0aaca1f5e69012d1feeda16d1e","tid":490252,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"比家用老母洗碗，唔洗做呀？"}]}